</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="235" pageNumber="514" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="235.[1376,2586,289,1230]" pageId="235" pageNumber="514">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1379,1728,1041,1070]" pageId="235" pageNumber="514">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List (as C. sorellus, and including C. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Osgood" authorityYear="1901" box="[1679,1768,1077,1110]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Microtus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="235" pageNumber="514" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="miurus">miurus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1842,1943,1077,1110]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Calomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="235" pageNumber="514" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="frida">C. frida</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
